"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[iftags +組件]]<br />\n[[note]]<br />\n**原文：**[http://topia.wikidot.com/sp-rate-info-2 Sp Rate Info 2] 和 [http://topia.wikidot.com/rate:rate-module-test-2 Rate Module Test 2]<br />\n------<br />\n**原作者：**[[*user 7happy7]]<br />\n[[/note]]<br />\n------<br />\n[[/iftags]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/component:black-highlighter-theme-dev\">component:black-highlighter-theme-dev</a>]]<br />\n[[iftags +組件]]<br />\n[[note]]<br />\n給我加分。。或者減分。<br />\n----<br />\n+* [*http://topia.wikidot.com/rate:rate-module-test Sigma-9 版本]<br />\n[[/note]]<br />\n<br />\n[[&gt;]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-sandbox2-zh.wikidot.com/component:sp-rate-info-2\">:scp-sandbox2-zh:component:sp-rate-info-2</a> start= --]|bhl=true]]<br />\n**新評分模組！**<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-sandbox2-zh.wikidot.com/component:sp-rate-info-2\">:scp-sandbox2-zh:component:sp-rate-info-2</a> end= --]]]<br />\n[[/&gt;]]<br />\n&gt; [[include component:black-highlighter-theme-dev]]<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; @@[[&gt;]]@@<br />\n&gt; [[include component:sp-rate-info-2 start= @@--@@]|bhl=true]]<br />\n&gt; **新評分模組！**<br />\n&gt; [[include component:sp-rate-info-2 end= @@--@@]]]<br />\n&gt; @@[[/&gt;]]@@<br />\n<br />\n[[&gt;]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-sandbox2-zh.wikidot.com/component:sp-rate-info-2\">:scp-sandbox2-zh:component:sp-rate-info-2</a> start= --]|end= --]|info=none|bhl=true]]<br />\n[[/&gt;]]<br />\n&gt; [[include component:black-highlighter-theme-dev]]<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; @@[[&gt;]]@@<br />\n&gt; [[include component:sp-rate-info-2 start= @@--]|end= --@@]|info=none|bhl=true]]<br />\n&gt; @@[[/&gt;]]@@<br />\n[[/iftags]]<br />\n<br />\n[!-- {$start}<br />\n[[module CSS]]<br />\n.rate_t2 .mod_info {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .mod_info .creditRate {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: none;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .credit {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;overflow: scroll;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 35vh;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: #633;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border: solid 1px #633;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-spacing: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-radius: 5px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;box-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.5);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: inline-block;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: linear-gradient(0deg,hsla(0,0%,66.7%,.25) 0,hsla(0,0%,66.7%,.15));<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(var(--swatch-menubg-medium-color),.25) 0,rgba(var(--swatch-menubg-medium-color),.15));<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: #fcfcfc;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgb(var(--swatch-background));<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border: .0625rem solid rgba(12,12,12,.25);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border: .0625rem solid rgba(var(--swatch-menubg-black-color),.25);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-radius: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;box-shadow: 0.0625rem 0.0625rem 0 rgba(12,12,12,.15);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;box-shadow: .0625rem .0625rem 0 rgba(var(--swatch-menubg-black-color),0.15);<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.rate_t2 .main_rate {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;box-shadow: unset;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-radius: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-bottom: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-right: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border: none;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: transparent;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box &gt; span {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border: none;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-radius: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .rate-points,<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .cancel {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: transparent!important;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .cancel {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding-left: 0.4em;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .cancel a {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: #fff6f0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: inline-block;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;font-family: 'FontAwesome';<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;font-weight: 400;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;font-size: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .cancel a {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: #0c0c0c;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: rgb(var(--rating-module-button-color));<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .cancel a:before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;content: '\\f00d';<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;font-size: 0.8rem;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .cancel a:before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgb(12,12,12);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgb(var(--rating-module-text-color));<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.rate_t2 .t_info div {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;position: relative;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 24px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 20px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;top: 1px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding: 0 0 0 2px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-left: 1px solid #966;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 .t_info div {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-color: rgba(12,12,12,.25);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-color: rgba(var(--swatch-menubg-black-color),.25);<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .t_info div a {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: #fff6f0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: flex;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;align-items: center;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;justify-content: center;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 100%;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 100%;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 .t_info div a {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: #0c0c0c;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: rgb(var(--rating-module-button-color));<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .t_info div a:before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;position: relative;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;top: -0.5px;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .page-rate-widget-box .cancel a:hover,<br />\n.rate_t2 .t_info div a:hover {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;color: #966;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;text-decoration: none;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.rate_t2 .list-pages-box .list-pages-item {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-radius: 2px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;overflow: hidden;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .line_ud {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: inline-block;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 4px;<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .line_ud:first-of-type {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: lightgreen;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 .line_ud:first-of-type {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: rgba(0,200,0,.8);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: rgba(var(--rating-module-button-plus-color),.8);<br />\n}<br />\n.rate_t2 .line_ud:last-of-type {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: pink;<br />\n}<br />\n.bhl-true.rate_t2 .line_ud:last-of-type {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: rgba(200,0,0,.8);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: rgba(var(--rating-module-button-negative-color),.8);<br />\n}<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\n[[table class=&quot;rate_t2 bhl-{$bhl}&quot;]]<br />\n[[row]]<br />\n[[cell class=&quot;main_rate&quot;]]<br />\n[[module Rate]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[cell class=&quot;t_info&quot; rowspan=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;display: {$info};&quot;]]<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[a href=&quot;#u-credit-view&quot; class=&quot;fa fa-info&quot;]][[image http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wikidot.com/local--files/nav:side/blank.png title=&quot;Show Info&quot; style=&quot;position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;top:0;left:0;&quot;]][[/a]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[/row]]<br />\n<br />\n[[row]]<br />\n[[cell]]<br />\n[[module ListPages name=&quot;=&quot;]]<br />\n[[div_ style=&quot;display:[[#ifexpr %%rating_votes%% == 0 | none | block ]];&quot;]]<br />\n[[span class=&quot;line_ud&quot; style=&quot;width: [[#expr (%%rating%%+%%rating_votes%%)/2/%%rating_votes%%*100]]%;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/span]][[span class=&quot;line_ud&quot; style=&quot;width: [[#expr (%%rating_votes%%-%%rating%%)/2/%%rating_votes%%*100]]%;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/span]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div_ style=&quot;display:[[#ifexpr %%rating_votes%% == 0 | block | none ]];&quot;]]<br />\n[[span class=&quot;line_ud&quot; style=&quot;width: 100%;background: grey;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/span]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[/row]]<br />\n<br />\n[[row]]<br />\n[[cell class=&quot;mod_info&quot;]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:start-standalone\">info:start-standalone</a>]]<br />\n[!----]<br />\n<br />\n[!-- {$end}<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:end-standalone\">info:end-standalone</a>]]<br />\n[[/cell]]<br />\n[[/row]]<br />\n[[/table]]<br />\n[!----]\n</div>\n"